1. What is Replit?

Replit is a cloud-based online IDE (Integrated Development Environment) where you can write, run, test, and deploy applications directly from your browser.

Unlike traditional development, you don't need to install Python, Flask, or VS Code on your local computer.

Everything runs in the cloud.

